WENDEL v. HOFFMAN et al. No. 7078. Circuit Court of Appeals, Third Circuit. May 16, 1939. Thomas L. Zimmerman, Jr., of Ridge-wood, N.J., for appellant. *57Harry Green, of Newark, N. J., for ap-pellees.

Before BIGGS and MARIS, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The appeal is dismissed for failure to comply with the provisions of Federal Civil Procedure Rule 73(g), 28 U.S.C.A. following section 723c,
